{
  "stem": "15393.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She brought this badge, R, for my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother went back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm now going to shorten this thing, because it was very difficult for me to let my mother go on her own.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was quite pleased to leave me in a safe place, because this was as safe a place as you could ever find.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But for me, to-- to see her go was terrible and to the ghetto and-- and no communication with the ghetto, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, on the assumption, that she will be coming every Saturday evening, stay over Sunday, and Monday morning, in the wee hours, she'll leave about 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She would have to go through the entire town, from one end to the town to the-- to the other, to the ghetto, to join some working group and walk through the town, without armband, without that thing on, join a group, put this on, all of it, and into the ghetto, so that she may, from the ghetto, go out to work again.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, can you visualize?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no way, through the whole week, that I knew whether my mother was alive or not, whether my grandparents were alive or not.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I couldn't bear being there, in this safe place, on my own, most of the day, because she was at work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was neither here nor there, because I didn't feel like talking with her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anyway, I didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I suddenly spoke it, out of the blue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't speak it there and then yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all I wanted was to go-- to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was locked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She locked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
